        <p align="center"><b>Heart Strong</b></p>
        <p align="justify">There are many lessons to be learned from Ateneo’s recent win. Despite being a neophyte team, the Lady Eagles never gave up on themselves and simply refused to lose. The team showed how unity, a strong heart and firm resolve can negate handicaps and overcome the most daunting challenges.</p>
        <p>As a nation, we believe that this is something that we have started to show. We overcame disheartening obstacles in the past through perseverance and dedication. Although we enjoy newfound adoration from the international community, it is clear that much more has to be done to make our economic growth more inclusive. Instead of resorting to nay-saying and crab mentality, we should focus on achieving more by uniting for common causes. And as we have seen in the championship run of the Lady Eagles, believing in ourselves and having a strong heart will allow us to move forward faster and achieve seemingly impossible feats.</p>
        

        
        
